txt.en: You have weakened the masts of many Corsair ships at Ethillorn.
You have weakened the masts of many Corsair ships docked at Ethillorn. While they may not notice your efforts now, their masts shall topple when the wind catches their unfurled sails.
Corsair ships can be found at the docks of Ethillorn in western Lower Lebennin.\n\nYou have found many Corsair ships at Ethillorn and should weaken their masts before they set sail once more.
After reaching the docks of Ethillorn, you notice several large Corsair ships docked in the harbour. You should weaken their masts to strand the Corsairs on the coastline before you depart the ruins.
